<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>4</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p class="">표현이 너무 단순해서 따로 설명할 필요가 없네요.</p></div></details></li></ul></div>
</div></details></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>정답</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p class="">1</p></div></details></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>해설</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul class="toggle"><li><details open=""><summary>해석문</summary><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p>'Memories bring back, memories bring back you'은 이 곡의 감성과 메시지를 담은 핵심 가사 중 하나입니다.</p></div></details></li></ul></div></div></details></li></ul></div></div></details></li></ul></div>

</div></details></div>

</div></article></body></html>